OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has
OL,7,Fconfirmed he has asked for a decision
OL,8,Fto cancel summer schemes at special
OL,9,Fschools in Northern Ireland to be
OL,10,Frevisited.
OL,12,FIt comes as it is confirmed MLAs will
OL,13,Fbe recalled from their Easter break
OL,14,Ffollowing widespread criticism of the
OL,15,Fdecision.
OL,17,FThe Alliance Party has tabled a recall
OL,18,Fmotion at the Assembly after
OL,19,Fdescribing the move as "nothing short
OL,20,Fof disgraceful".
OL,26,@{D@XOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FIt emerged on Thursday that the
OL,7,Fschemes, which provide support for
OL,8,Fchildren with additional needs over
OL,9,Fthe summer, would not go ahead in 2026
OL,10,Fover concerns about the healthcare
OL,11,Favailable for pupils.
OL,13,FAn Assembly committee heard on
OL,14,FThursday that families are "spitting
OL,15,Ffire" over the decision.
OL,17,FThe Education Authority (EA) said it
OL,18,Fhad attempted to avoid the move
OL,19,Fthrough repeated engagement with the
OL,20,FDepartment of Health.
OL,26,@vD@\OUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FFollowing a meeting with the EA on
OL,7,FFriday, Mr Givan said: "Decisions
OL,8,Fregarding the operation of summer
OL,9,Fschemes in special schools rests with
OL,10,Fthe EA.
OL,12,F"However, given the profound impact
OL,13,Fthat the cancellation of these schemes
OL,14,Fwill have on children, young people
OL,15,Fand their families, I have asked the
OL,16,FEA to engage further with the
OL,17,FDepartment of Health to review the
OL,18,Fposition and to explore all possible
OL,19,Favenues to provide summer schemes for
OL,20,Fas many children as possible.
OL,26,@oD@XOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,F"If the Department of Health can
OL,7,Fprovide the necessary clinical and
OL,8,Fnursing support, the Education
OL,9,FAuthority has confirmed that it stands
OL,10,Fready to deliver summer schemes this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"Further engagement will also be
OL,14,Frequired with special school leaders."
OL,16,FHe added: "Our shared objective is to
OL,17,Fensure that children with the most
OL,18,Fcomplex needs are not left without
OL,19,Fvital support and that families have
OL,20,Fconfidence in the services designed to
OL,21,Fassist them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUvD@fO]xD@KOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt said it
OL,7,Fwas "simply unthinkable that young
OL,8,Fpeople themselves should lose out on
OL,9,Fthe enjoyment of the summer school
OL,10,Fenvironment".
OL,12,FHe continued: "I have therefore tasked
OL,13,Fthe Permanent Secretary to urgently
OL,14,Fexplore how a suitable and appropriate
OL,15,Fprovision could be put in place."
OL,26,@oD@EOUrD@LO]tD@OOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FMLAs will return to the Assembly on
OL,7,FTuesday to debate a motion expressing
OL,8,F"grave concern" over the cancellation
OL,9,Fof the summer schemes, following a
OL,10,Frecall motion submitted by the
OL,11,FAlliance Party.
OL,13,FAlliance MLA Eoin Tennyson said: "The
OL,14,Fdecision to suspend summer schemes at
OL,15,Fspecial schools is nothing short of
OL,16,Fdisgraceful.
OL,18,F"That this announcement was dropped as
OL,19,Fthe Assembly enters Easter recess only
OL,20,Fadds insult to injury.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]uD@OrwuD@bOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,F"Once again, it is the most vulnerable
OL,7,Fchildren who are paying the price for
OL,8,Ffailure and inaction.
OL,10,F"Parents are being left abandoned,
OL,11,Fscrambling for alternatives that
OL,12,Fsimply do not exist.
OL,14,F"The response from the Education and
OL,15,FHealth Ministers has been woefully
OL,16,Finadequate."
OL,18,FMr Tennyson said the ministers needed
OL,19,Fto provide answers to the Assembly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FSinn Fein MLA Cathy Mason confirmed
OL,7,Fher party would be supporting the
OL,8,FAlliance motion.
OL,10,FShe said: "The decision to stop these
OL,11,Fschemes is deplorable and has caused
OL,12,Funnecessary angst among parents and
OL,13,Fvulnerable children who rely heavily
OL,14,Fon this lifeline.
OL,16,F"The political blame game between the
OL,17,FDUP and UUP ministers in the aftermath
OL,18,Fis disgraceful and only fuels further
OL,19,Fconcern and confusion.
OL,21,F"Families deserve better."
OL,26,@nD@GrrrD@KOUxD@AOU}D@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
