FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FUlster Unionist leader Jon Burrows
OL,7,Fsaid the summer schemes "provide vital
OL,8,Fstructure, care and respite".
OL,10,FHe said: "For the EA to make this
OL,11,Fannouncement on the eve of the Easter
OL,12,Frecess shows a clear and deliberate
OL,13,Flack of accountability."
OL,15,FTUV MLA Timothy Gaston said the
OL,16,Fdecision to cancel special school
OL,17,Fsummer schemes has "rightly caused
OL,18,Fanger among families across Northern
OL,19,FIreland".
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@\O]rD@JOUuD@XO]yD@TOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FHe added: "These schemes are not a
OL,7,Fluxury ` they are a lifeline,
OL,8,Fproviding vital support for children
OL,9,Fwith complex needs and essential
OL,10,Frespite for parents.
OL,12,F"Both the Education and Health
OL,13,FMinisters owe the public an
OL,14,Fexplanation.
OL,16,F"As has already been highlighted,
OL,17,Fvulnerable children have effectively
OL,18,Fbeen left in the lurch as a result of
OL,19,Fwhat appears to be a failure of
OL,20,Fcoordination between departments.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,F"It is simply not acceptable that,
OL,7,Fwith months still to go before the
OL,8,Fsummer, Stormont has allowed this
OL,9,Fprovision to collapse without a clear
OL,10,Falternative in place."
OL,12,FOn Thursday, the EA said it had "made
OL,13,Fclear" that on-site nursing cover
OL,14,Fwould be required for summer schemes
OL,15,Fto be held safely.
OL,17,FHowever, the authority said the
OL,18,FDepartment of Health had confirmed
OL,19,Fthis will not be available.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]tD@aOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1774803956
OL,3,CGivan asks for cancellation of special
OL,4,Cschool summer schemes to be 'revisited'
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Education
OL,7,FAuthority said: "This decision has
OL,8,Fbeen taken solely on safety grounds.
OL,10,F"We deeply regret it and fully
OL,11,Funderstand that it will be very
OL,12,Fdistressing for children and parents."
OL,14,FSpeaking later, Health Minister Mike
OL,15,FNesbitt said contingency plans were
OL,16,Fbeing examined.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
